{"id":121,"parent_id":95,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":121,"title":"Acts 26","subtitle":"","short_title":"Acts","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 26"],[".studySummary",["i","Paul recounts his former persecution of the Saints as a Pharisee—He testifies of the appearance of Jesus on the Damascus road—Paul bears his testimony to King Agrippa."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.1","order":"03.07.026.14584"},["b","1"],"Then Agrippa said unto Paul, Thou art permitted to speak for thyself. Then Paul stretched forth the hand, and answered for himself:"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.2","order":"03.07.026.14585"},["b","2"],"I think myself happy, king Agrippa, because I shall answer for myself this day before thee touching all the things whereof I am accused of the Jews:"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.3","order":"03.07.026.14586"},["b","3"],"Especially",["i","because I know"],"thee to be expert in all customs and questions which are among the Jews: wherefore I beseech thee to hear me patiently."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.4","order":"03.07.026.14587"},["b","4"],"My manner of life from my youth, which was at the first among mine own nation at Jerusalem, know all the Jews;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.5","order":"03.07.026.14588"},["b","5"],"Which knew me from the beginning, if they would testify, that after the most straitest sect of our religion I lived a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Pharisee"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.6","order":"03.07.026.14589"},["b","6"],"And now I stand and am judged for the hope of the promise made of God unto our fathers:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.7","order":"03.07.026.14590"},["b","7"],"Unto which",["i","promise"],"our",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"twelve tribes"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"instantly"],"serving",["i","God"],"day and night, hope to come. For which hope’s sake, king Agrippa, I am accused of the Jews."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.8","order":"03.07.026.14591"},["b","8"],"Why should it be thought a thing incredible with you, that God should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"raise"],"the dead?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.9","order":"03.07.026.14592"},["b","9"],"I verily thought with myself, that I ought to do many things",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"contrary"],"to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"name"],"of Jesus of Nazareth."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.10","order":"03.07.026.14593"},["b","10"],"Which thing I also did in Jerusalem: and many of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"saints"],"did I shut up in prison, having received authority from the chief priests; and when they were put to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"death"],", I gave my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_10c"},"voice"],"against",["i","them."]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.11","order":"03.07.026.14594"},["b","11"],"And I punished them oft in every synagogue, and compelled",["i","them"],"to blaspheme; and being exceedingly mad against them, I persecuted",["i","them"],"even unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"strange"],"cities."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.12","order":"03.07.026.14595"},["b","12"],"Whereupon as I went to Damascus with authority and commission from the chief priests,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.13","order":"03.07.026.14596"},["b","13"],"At midday, O king, I saw in the way a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"light"],"from heaven, above the brightness of the sun, shining round about me and them which journeyed with me."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.14","order":"03.07.026.14597"},["b","14"],"And when we were all fallen to the earth, I heard a voice speaking unto me, and saying in the Hebrew tongue,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Saul"],", Saul, why persecutest thou me?",["i","it is"],"hard for thee to kick",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"against"],"the pricks."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.15","order":"03.07.026.14598"},["b","15"],"And I said, Who art thou, Lord? And he said, I am Jesus whom thou persecutest."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.16","order":"03.07.026.14599"},["b","16"],"But rise, and stand upon thy feet: for I have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"appeared"],"unto thee for this purpose, to make thee a minister and a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"witness"],"both of these things which thou hast seen, and of those things in the which I will appear unto thee;"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.17","order":"03.07.026.14600"},["b","17"],"Delivering thee from the people, and",["i","from"],"the Gentiles, unto whom now I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"send"],"thee,"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.18","order":"03.07.026.14601"},["b","18"],"To open their eyes,",["i","and"],"to turn",["i","them"],"from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"darkness"],"to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"light"],", and",["i","from"],"the power of Satan unto God, that they may receive forgiveness of sins, and inheritance among them which are sanctified by faith that is in me."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.19","order":"03.07.026.14602"},["b","19"],"Whereupon, O king Agrippa, I was not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"disobedient"],"unto the heavenly",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"vision"],":"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.20","order":"03.07.026.14603"},["b","20"],"But shewed first unto them of Damascus, and at Jerusalem, and throughout all the coasts of Judæa, and",["i","then"],"to the Gentiles, that they should repent and turn to God, and do works meet for repentance."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.21","order":"03.07.026.14604"},["b","21"],"For these causes the Jews caught me in the temple, and went about to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"kill"],["i","me."]],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.22","order":"03.07.026.14605"},["b","22"],"Having therefore obtained help of God, I continue unto this day, witnessing both to small and great, saying none other things than those which the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"prophets"],"and Moses did say should come:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.23","order":"03.07.026.14606"},["b","23"],"That Christ should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"suffer"],",",["i","and"],"that he should be the first that should",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"rise"],"from the dead, and should shew light unto the people, and to the Gentiles."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.24","order":"03.07.026.14607"},["b","24"],"And as he thus spake for himself, Festus said with a loud voice, Paul, thou art beside thyself; much learning doth make thee",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"mad"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.25","order":"03.07.026.14608"},["b","25"],"But he said, I am not mad, most noble Festus; but speak forth the words of truth and soberness."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.26","order":"03.07.026.14609"},["b","26"],"For the king knoweth of these things, before whom also I speak freely: for I am persuaded that none of these things are hidden from him; for this thing was not done in a corner."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.27","order":"03.07.026.14610"},["b","27"],"King Agrippa, believest thou the prophets? I know that thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"believest"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.28","order":"03.07.026.14611"},["b","28"],"Then Agrippa said unto Paul, Almost thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"persuadest"],"me to be a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_28b"},"Christian"],"."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.29","order":"03.07.026.14612"},["b","29"],"And Paul said, I would to God, that not only thou, but also all that hear me this day, were both almost, and altogether such as I am, except these bonds."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.30","order":"03.07.026.14613"},["b","30"],"And when he had thus spoken, the king rose up, and the governor, and Bernice, and they that sat with them:"],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.31","order":"03.07.026.14614"},["b","31"],"And when they were gone aside, they talked between themselves, saying, This man doeth nothing worthy of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"death"],"or of bonds."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.32","order":"03.07.026.14615"},["b","32"],"Then said Agrippa unto Festus, This man might have been set at liberty, if he had not appealed unto",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_32a"},"Cæsar"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.5a","order":"03.07.026.14616"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.3"},"Acts 22:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/23.6.6-9"},"23:6 (6–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.7a","order":"03.07.026.14618"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-twelve-tribes-of"},"TG Israel, Twelve Tribes of"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.7b","order":"03.07.026.14620"},["b","7b"],["span.small","GR"],"earnestly, intently."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.8a","order":"03.07.026.14622"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/resurrection"},"TG Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.9a","order":"03.07.026.14624"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/1.13"},"1 Tim. 1:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.9b","order":"03.07.026.14626"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/name"},"TG Name"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.10a","order":"03.07.026.14628"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.1,13.13-14"},"Acts 9:1, 13 (13–14)"],",",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.21"},"21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.4.4-5"},"22:4 (4–5)"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.10b","order":"03.07.026.14630"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"10c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.10c","order":"03.07.026.14632"},["b","10c"],["span.small","GR"],"vote."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.11a","order":"03.07.026.14634"},["b","11a"],["span.small","GR"],"foreign."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.13a","order":"03.07.026.14636"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.16"},"JS—H 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.14a","order":"03.07.026.14638"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.4.1-9"},"Acts 9:4 (1–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.7.6-16"},"22:7 (6–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.14b","order":"03.07.026.14640"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/opposition"},"TG Opposition"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.16a","order":"03.07.026.14642"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-appearances-postmortal"},"TG Jesus Christ, Appearances, Postmortal"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.16b","order":"03.07.026.14644"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.2"},"Luke 1:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.14"},"John 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/5.32"},"Acts 5:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/9.15"},"9:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.15"},"22:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/14.8"},"D&C 14:8"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.17a","order":"03.07.026.14646"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/22.21"},"Acts 22:21"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.18a","order":"03.07.026.14648"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-in-darkness"},"TG Walking in Darkness"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.18b","order":"03.07.026.14650"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/light-noun"},"TG Light [noun]"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.19a","order":"03.07.026.14652"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disobedience"},"TG Disobedience"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.19b","order":"03.07.026.14654"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.21a","order":"03.07.026.14656"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/21.31.30-31"},"Acts 21:31 (30–31)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.22a","order":"03.07.026.14658"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/28.23"},"Acts 28:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.23a","order":"03.07.026.14660"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.23b","order":"03.07.026.14662"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.24a","order":"03.07.026.14664"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.24.24-25"},"JS—H 1:24 (24–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.27a","order":"03.07.026.14666"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/30.42.41-42"},"Alma 30:42 (41–42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.28a","order":"03.07.026.14668"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/missionary-work"},"TG Missionary Work"],"."],["div",{"id":"28b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.28b","order":"03.07.026.14670"},["b","28b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/11.26"},"Acts 11:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.31a","order":"03.07.026.14672"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/capital-punishment"},"TG Capital Punishment"],"."],["div",{"id":"32a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/acts/26.32a","order":"03.07.026.14674"},["b","32a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/acts/25.11"},"Acts 25:11"],"."]]}
